item.title: Me-So Twisted - The Sound of Tongue Tied 'N' Twisted pt1
item.description: Taking 2 records representitive of their sound, Meso Twisted (the TTNT crew's collective DJ monkier) takes you on a journey through our dj's favourite tracks. 10 tracks = 52 mins We hope you enjoy ;-) 1 - Mr On v's The Jungle Brothers - Breathe, Don't stop 2 - Basement Jaxx - Do your thing (Gadjo remix) 3 - La Tour - Blue (Nush me club mix) 4 - Solar Plexus - Omargarashid (mk1) 5 - Mory Kante - Yeke Yeke 6 - Ty Tek feat Cat Conger - Killing me 7 - Aquasky & Rob Le Pitch - Wasted music 8 - Backdraft - Poledancer 9 - Peter Paul - More Tekila 10 - Noisia - Gutterpump Track selection 1 & 2 - Just call me Joel 3 & 4 - Domingo 5 & 6 - erik.b 7 & 8 - Spanish 9 & 10 - DJ Ellan Mixed by erik.b Produced by erik.b, DJ Ellan and Spanish
